Chapel is a programming language for HPC that has modern comforts.
https://chapel-lang.org

Now that Chapel drives GPUs, let's rewrite Chicken in Chapel.

We will continue to use the Python pre- and post-processing
tools from the chiken (in CUDA) directory, for the moment.
We will probably port those tools to use the Python Arkouda
project in time.

Peter J. 2024-01-23

